{
  "id": 2955,
  "name": "Resina effimera",
  "desc": "<p>An item that can be used to replenish Original Resin. Once used, it will replenish 60 Original Resin.</p><p>Once obtained, it will automatically dissipate after a period of time.</p><p></p><p>· The expiration time will be calculated from the Monday after this item is obtained, and it will disappear seven days from then.</p><p>· Multiple Transient Resins obtained on different weeks will have their expiration dates counted independently.</p><p></p><p>Pure energy that will dissipate with time. In this, it is similar to all else that is lovely in this world. But seize this opportunity and go make the world a slightly better place, as is fitting for one who dwells within the bounds of \"time.\"</p>",
